#

Balsamic Glazed Tomato Toast

15 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVegan

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

QuickLightSnack

Description

A delightful and easy-to-make open-faced sandwich featuring fresh tomatoes drizzled with a rich balsamic glaze, perfect as a snack or light meal.

Ingredients

  • sourdough bread: 2 slices
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • balsamic glaze: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh basil leaves: a handful
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
